<div class="chapter ch1" data-usfm="SNG.1">
  <div class="label">1</div>
  <div class="p">
    <span class="content"> </span><span class="verse v1" data-usfm="SNG.1.1"><span class="label">1</span><span
      class="content"> </span><span class="pn"><span class="content">所罗门</span></span><span class="content">的歌，是歌中的雅歌。</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="s">
    <span class="heading">第一首</span>
  </div>
  <div class="sp">
    <span class="heading">〔新娘〕</span>
  </div>
  <div class="q1">
    <span class="verse v1" data-usfm="SNG.1.1"><span class="content"> </span></span><span class="verse v2"
      data-usfm="SNG.1.2"><span class="label">2</span><span class="content">愿他用口与我亲嘴；</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="q1">
    <span class="verse v2" data-usfm="SNG.1.2"><span class="content">因你的爱情比酒更美。</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="q1">
    <span class="verse v2" data-usfm="SNG.1.2"><span class="content"> </span></span><span class="verse v3"
      data-usfm="SNG.1.3"><span class="label">3</span><span class="content">你的膏油馨香；</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="q1">
    <span class="verse v3" data-usfm="SNG.1.3"><span class="content">你的名</span><span class="add"><span
        class="content">如同</span></span><span class="content">倒出来的</span><span class="add"><span class="content">香</span></span><span
      class="content">膏，</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="q1">
    <span class="verse v3" data-usfm="SNG.1.3"><span class="content">所以众童女都爱你。</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="q1">
    <span class="verse v3" data-usfm="SNG.1.3"><span class="content"> </span></span><span class="verse v4"
      data-usfm="SNG.1.4"><span class="label">4</span><span class="content">愿你吸引我，我们就快跑跟随你。</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="q1">
    <span class="verse v4" data-usfm="SNG.1.4"><span class="content">王带我进了内室，</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="q1">
    <span class="verse v4" data-usfm="SNG.1.4"><span class="content">我们必因你欢喜快乐。</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="q1">
    <span class="verse v4" data-usfm="SNG.1.4"><span class="content">我们要称赞你的爱情，</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="q1">
    <span class="verse v4" data-usfm="SNG.1.4"><span class="content">胜似称赞</span><span class="add"><span
        class="content">美</span></span><span class="content">酒。</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="q1">
    <span class="verse v4" data-usfm="SNG.1.4"><span class="content">他们爱你是理所当然的。</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="q1">
    <span class="verse v4" data-usfm="SNG.1.4"><span class="content"> </span></span><span class="verse v5"
      data-usfm="SNG.1.5"><span class="label">5</span><span class="content"> </span><span class="pn"><span
        class="content">耶路撒冷</span></span><span class="content">的众女子啊，</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="q1">
    <span class="verse v5" data-usfm="SNG.1.5"><span class="content">我虽然黑，却是秀美，</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="q1">
    <span class="verse v5" data-usfm="SNG.1.5"><span class="content">如同</span><span class="pn"><span
        class="content">基达</span></span><span class="content">的帐棚，</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="q1">
    <span class="verse v5" data-usfm="SNG.1.5"><span class="content">好像</span><span class="pn"><span
        class="content">所罗门</span></span><span class="content">的幔子。</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="q1">
    <span class="verse v5" data-usfm="SNG.1.5"><span class="content"> </span></span><span class="verse v6"
      data-usfm="SNG.1.6"><span class="label">6</span><span class="content">不要因日头把我晒黑了就轻看我。</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="q1">
    <span class="verse v6" data-usfm="SNG.1.6"><span class="content">我同母的弟兄向我发怒，</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="q1">
    <span class="verse v6" data-usfm="SNG.1.6"><span class="content">他们使我看守葡萄园；</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="q1">
    <span class="verse v6" data-usfm="SNG.1.6"><span class="content">我自己的葡萄园却没有看守。</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="q1">
    <span class="verse v6" data-usfm="SNG.1.6"><span class="content"> </span></span><span class="verse v7"
      data-usfm="SNG.1.7"><span class="label">7</span><span class="content">我心所爱的啊，求你告诉我，</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="q1">
    <span class="verse v7" data-usfm="SNG.1.7"><span class="content">你在何处牧羊？</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="q1">
    <span class="verse v7" data-usfm="SNG.1.7"><span class="content">晌午在何处使羊歇卧？</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="q1">
    <span class="verse v7" data-usfm="SNG.1.7"><span class="content">我何必在你同伴的羊群旁边</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="q1">
    <span class="verse v7" data-usfm="SNG.1.7"><span class="content">好像蒙着脸的人呢？</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="sp">
    <span class="heading">〔新郎〕</span>
  </div>
  <div class="q1">
    <span class="verse v7" data-usfm="SNG.1.7"><span class="content"> </span></span><span class="verse v8"
      data-usfm="SNG.1.8"><span class="label">8</span><span class="content">你这女子中极美丽的，</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="q1">
    <span class="verse v8" data-usfm="SNG.1.8"><span class="content">你若不知道，</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="q1">
    <span class="verse v8" data-usfm="SNG.1.8"><span class="content">只管跟随羊群的脚踪去，</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="q1">
    <span class="verse v8" data-usfm="SNG.1.8"><span class="content">把你的山羊羔牧放在牧人帐棚的旁边。</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="q1">
    <span class="verse v8" data-usfm="SNG.1.8"><span class="content"> </span></span><span class="verse v9"
      data-usfm="SNG.1.9"><span class="label">9</span><span class="content">我的佳偶，</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="q1">
    <span class="verse v9" data-usfm="SNG.1.9"><span class="content">我将你比法老车上套的骏马。</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="q1">
    <span class="verse v9" data-usfm="SNG.1.9"><span class="content"> </span></span><span class="verse v10"
      data-usfm="SNG.1.10"><span class="label">10</span><span class="content">你的两腮因发辫而秀美；</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="q1">
    <span class="verse v10" data-usfm="SNG.1.10"><span class="content">你的颈项因珠串而华丽。</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="q1">
    <span class="verse v10" data-usfm="SNG.1.10"><span class="content"> </span></span><span class="verse v11"
      data-usfm="SNG.1.11"><span class="label">11</span><span class="content">我们要为你编上金辫，镶上银钉。</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="sp">
    <span class="heading">〔新娘〕</span>
  </div>
  <div class="q1">
    <span class="verse v11" data-usfm="SNG.1.11"><span class="content"> </span></span><span class="verse v12"
      data-usfm="SNG.1.12"><span class="label">12</span><span class="content">王正坐席的时候，</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="q1">
    <span class="verse v12" data-usfm="SNG.1.12"><span class="content">我的哪哒香膏发出香味。</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="q1">
    <span class="verse v12" data-usfm="SNG.1.12"><span class="content"> </span></span><span class="verse v13"
      data-usfm="SNG.1.13"><span class="label">13</span><span class="content">我以我的良人为一袋没药，</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="q1">
    <span class="verse v13" data-usfm="SNG.1.13"><span class="content">常在我怀中。</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="q1">
    <span class="verse v13" data-usfm="SNG.1.13"><span class="content"> </span></span><span class="verse v14"
      data-usfm="SNG.1.14"><span class="label">14</span><span class="content">我以我的良人为一棵凤仙花，</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="q1">
    <span class="verse v14" data-usfm="SNG.1.14"><span class="content">在</span><span class="pn"><span
        class="content">隐·基底</span></span><span class="content">葡萄园中。</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="sp">
    <span class="heading">〔新郎〕</span>
  </div>
  <div class="q1">
    <span class="verse v14" data-usfm="SNG.1.14"><span class="content"> </span></span><span class="verse v15"
      data-usfm="SNG.1.15"><span class="label">15</span><span class="content">我的佳偶，你甚美丽！你甚美丽！</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="q1">
    <span class="verse v15" data-usfm="SNG.1.15"><span class="content">你的眼</span><span class="add"><span
        class="content">好像</span></span><span class="content">鸽子眼。</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="sp">
    <span class="heading">〔新娘〕</span>
  </div>
  <div class="q1">
    <span class="verse v15" data-usfm="SNG.1.15"><span class="content"> </span></span><span class="verse v16"
      data-usfm="SNG.1.16"><span class="label">16</span><span class="content">我的良人哪，你甚美丽可爱！</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="q1">
    <span class="verse v16" data-usfm="SNG.1.16"><span class="content">我们以青草为床榻，</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="q1">
    <span class="verse v16" data-usfm="SNG.1.16"><span class="content"> </span></span><span class="verse v17"
      data-usfm="SNG.1.17"><span class="label">17</span><span class="content">以香柏树为房屋的栋梁，</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="q1">
    <span class="verse v17" data-usfm="SNG.1.17"><span class="content">以松树为椽子。</span></span>
  </div>
</div>